metadata.name: Rooftop range
metadata.description:
This image was taken during the lockdown of 2020, I was moored up in a small town in the south east of the UK.
The feeling of being trapped and constrained was quite profound, and so I started to look for interesting views and scenes in my local surroundings. 
A combination of night time and mist helps to create strange and unusual environment, even in a place I am very familiar with.
